&lt;h1 id="conclusion"&gt;Conclusion
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mermaid is truly &lt;strong&gt;powerful&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;flexible&lt;/strong&gt;; it provides us with many &lt;strong&gt;options&lt;/strong&gt; to draw various types of diagrams. However, in this short article, I couldn&amp;rsquo;t introduce all those options to you. If you need more details, you can refer to the Mermaid documentation linked in each title section. I hope you now have an overview of Mermaid and can apply it in your projects or your team&amp;rsquo;s projects, helping save time and effort.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>